headline: 3 Dividend Stocks to Double Up on Right Now
summary: With that advice in mind, right now is a great time to consider adding to your positions in Coca-Cola (NYSE: KO), NextEra Energy (NYSE: NEE), and Vici Properties (NYSE: VICI).  Coca-Cola has been a fantastic dividend stock over the years.  The beverage giant recently declared its latest dividend payment.
